gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 113, Raptors 103
gameRecap.excerpt: Orlando defeats Toronto, 113-103. For Orlando, Franz Wagner led the way with 19 points, seven rebounds, four assists, and two steals while aided by Paolo Banchero (17 points, nine rebounds, eight assists) in the victory. Gary Trent Jr. finished with a season-high 31 points and four rebounds with Jordan Nwora adding 14 points (three 3PM) and five rebounds for Toronto in the losing effort. Orlando improves to 39-28, while Toronto moves to 23-44 in the loss.
